com.localytics.android

Class InboxDetailFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.app.Fragment
      • com.localytics.android.InboxDetailFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener

    public final class InboxDetailFragment
extends android.app.Fragment
    Fragment class that displays an inbox campaign's full creative. This Fragment also handles tagging impression events when a call to action is tapped within the creative or when the Fragment is paused. Create a new instance using newInstance(InboxCampaign).

    Customization options:

    • Creative error callback: InboxDetailCallback
